{"tid":2267720,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"香港重光日 罌粟花襟章 紀念香港保衛戰中死去的英聯邦士兵","createTime":"2020-11-02T09:34:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-02T10:48:14.000Z","uid":33263,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"ea0a46078f97609875cb32f93dfb66fb715543b8","tid":2267720,"uid":33263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T09:34:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.wikiwand.com/zh-mo/%E5%9C%8B%E6%AE%A4%E7%BD%8C%E7%B2%9F%E8%8A%B1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.wikiwand.com%2Fzh-mo%2F%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%25AE%25A4%25E7%25BD%258C%25E7%25B2%259F%25E8%258A%25B1&d=Vpe8FAkBT2vLq%2FWrgjLHxY6aL69TDc1SPHZju%2B%2BXLiQ%3D&h=7a3e2896\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.wikiwand.com/zh-mo/%E5%9C%8B%E6%AE%A4%E7%BD%8C%E7%B2%9F%E8%8A%B1</a><br />\n<br />\n國殤罌粟花（英語：Remembrance poppy），即虞美人花（Papaver rhoeas），在1920年後，歐洲用來紀念在戰爭中過世的士兵的花朵。源自於1920年，因為《在法蘭德斯戰場》（In Flanders Fields）這首詩中[1]，提及在第一次世界大戰戰場上的罌粟花，美國軍團（American Legion）因此以罌粟花來紀念在第一次世界大戰中過世的美國軍人。英國、加拿大、澳大利亞與新西蘭的退伍軍人，也採納這個習俗。在國殤紀念日，加拿大與英國的政府官員及國民，會以佩帶罌粟花來紀念在第一次世界大戰中捐軀的軍人[2]。"},{"pid":"782655734ae85174a7706e093409e4d6ae8e2ace","tid":2267720,"uid":33263,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T09:34:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/a/a3/Royal_British_Legion%27s_Paper_Poppy_-_white_background.jpg/440px-Royal_British_Legion%27s_Paper_Poppy_-_white_background.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2Fthumb%2Fa%2Fa3%2FRoyal_British_Legion%2527s_Paper_Poppy_-_white_background.jpg%2F440px-Royal_British_Legion%2527s_Paper_Poppy_-_white_background.jpg&h=2265fb77&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"75120003e138e85074e8345731b7210726094a78","tid":2267720,"uid":228955,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T09:34:54.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"ff3c2f10be7f2fa5a14fc2c7fa8973d048f035d8","tid":2267720,"uid":91771,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":